== 事故與爭議 ==
*智利在小組賽第二場與墨西哥以3-3打平後，總教練[[豪爾赫·桑保利|豪爾赫·桑保利]]決定在16日讓球員們休假調整狀況，所有球員在放假後，除[[阿圖羅·比達爾|阿圖羅·比達爾]]外皆在晚上晚上9點回到胡安·平托·杜蘭（Juan Pinto Durán）體育中心<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.24horas.cl/deportes/copaamerica2015/arturo-vidal-se-ve-involucrado-en-un-choque-durante-su-tarde-libre-1695629 |title=24horas |accessdate=2016-05-29 |archive-date=2016-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119122742/http://www.24horas.cl/deportes/copaamerica2015/arturo-vidal-se-ve-involucrado-en-un-choque-durante-su-tarde-libre-1695629 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。稍後得知，比達爾因酒後駕車而發生車禍，遭到智利警方逮捕<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.24horas.cl/deportes/copaamerica2015/vidal-queda-detenido-por-conducir-bajo-la-influencia-del-alcohol-1695892 |title=24horas |accessdate=2016-05-29 |archive-date=2016-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324052806/http://www.24horas.cl/deportes/copaamerica2015/vidal-queda-detenido-por-conducir-bajo-la-influencia-del-alcohol-1695892 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在警局錄口供到隔日才回到訓練場地。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cooperativa.cl/noticias/deportes/futbol/arturo-vidal/arturo-vidal-es-formalizado-en-juzgado-de-san-bernardo/2015-06-17/114707.html |title=24horas |accessdate=2016-05-29 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013042/http://www.cooperativa.cl/noticias/deportes/futbol/arturo-vidal/arturo-vidal-es-formalizado-en-juzgado-de-san-bernardo/2015-06-17/114707.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>之後比達爾的駕照被吊銷，並被判需支付損害賠償。在比達爾回到訓練場地後，儘管有報導指出總教練桑保利會因酒駕事故而將比達爾排除於參賽名單外，但最後證實總教練桑保利仍將比達爾放在參賽名單內<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.24horas.cl/deportes/copaamerica2015/sampaoli-mantiene-a-vidal-en-la-roja-lo-que-necesitamos-es-incluirlo-1696300 |title=24horas |accessdate=2016-05-29 |archive-date=2016-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320195912/http://www.24horas.cl/deportes/copaamerica2015/sampaoli-mantiene-a-vidal-en-la-roja-lo-que-necesitamos-es-incluirlo-1696300 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

*17日，哥倫比亞於小組賽以1-0擊敗巴西後，巴西前鋒[[內馬爾|內馬爾]]在賽後用球踢向哥倫比亞後衛[[巴勃羅·阿爾梅羅|巴勃羅·阿爾梅羅]]，並試圖用頭撞哥倫比亞後衛[[傑森·穆利洛|傑森·穆利洛]]，哥倫比亞前鋒[[卡路士·巴卡|卡路士·巴卡]]氣憤不過衝向內馬爾推了一下，結果內馬爾與巴卡雙雙被判紅牌<ref>{{cite web | url = http://sports.sinchew.com.my/node/49658 | title = 美洲杯‧巴西0比1負哥倫比亞‧內馬爾領紅卡 | publisher = ''星洲日報'' | date = 2015-06-18 | accessdate = 2015-07-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150706071909/http://sports.sinchew.com.my/node/49658 | archive-date = 2015-07-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/football/32832950|title=Copa America: FT: Brazil 0–1 Colombia|date=2015-06-17|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2016-05-29|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618010712/http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/football/32832950|dead-url=no}}</ref>，事後巴卡因此被禁賽2場，內馬爾則被禁賽4場。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33208871 | title = Neymar: Brazil striker banned for Copa America | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2015-06-19 | accessdate = 2015-06-20 | archive-date = 2015-06-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150620021956/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/football/33208871 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/sports/20150621/36621264/ | title = 內馬爾提前打包 禁賽4場加罰31萬 | publisher = ''蘋果日報'' | date = 2015-06-21 | accessdate = 2015-07-05 | archive-date = 2015-07-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150707021932/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/sports/20150621/36621264/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>賽後南美足協判內馬爾1萬美金罰金，並禁賽4場<ref>{{cite news|title=Neymar suspended for remainder of Copa America tournament|url=http://www.espnfc.com/copa-america/story/2498461/neymar-suspended-for-remainder-of-copa-america|accessdate=2015-06-19|publisher=ESPN|date=2015-06-19|archive-date=2015-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150620043609/http://www.espnfc.com/copa-america/story/2498461/neymar-suspended-for-remainder-of-copa-america|dead-url=no}}</ref>，巴卡則禁賽2場。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Macguire|first1=Eoghan|title=Copa America 2015: Neymar banned for remainder of tournament|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/20/football/copa-america-2015-neymar-ban/|accessdate=2015-07-23|publisher=CNN|date=2015-06-21|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724125100/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/20/football/copa-america-2015-neymar-ban/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

*在智利於半準決賽以1-0氣走上屆冠軍烏拉圭後，智利後衛{{le|岡薩洛·哈拉|Gonzalo Jara}}被拍到對烏拉圭前鋒[[埃丁森·卡瓦尼|埃丁森·卡瓦尼]]屁股做出不雅手勢，卡瓦尼氣到直接對哈拉掌摑，兩人最後都拿到黃牌，而卡瓦尼因先前抗議裁判判決已拿到一張黃牌，因而獲得一張紅牌遭到下場。賽後兩人被禁賽二場<ref>{{cite news|last1=Grez|first1=Matias|title=Copa America 2015: Gonzalo Jara's poke in backside earns him ban|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/29/football/football-jara-copa-america-ban-cavani/|accessdate=2015-07-23|publisher=CNN|date=2015-06-30|archive-date=2015-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724123544/http://edition.cnn.com/2015/06/29/football/football-jara-copa-america-ban-cavani/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=美洲杯比赛中掌掴对手 卡瓦尼被南美足联禁赛两场 |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/2015-07-29/16377665352.shtml |accessdate=2015-07-29 |work=新浪网 |date=2015-07-29 |archive-date=2016-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160701191312/http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/2015-07-29/16377665352.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，哈拉原屬球隊[[美因茨05|美因茨05]]對此行為表示不滿，宣稱要將哈拉交易出去。<ref>{{cite news|title=Angry Mainz to offload Gonzalo Jara for prodding Edinson Cavani’s bottom|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/jun/26/mainz-gonzalo-jara-edinson-cavani-bottom|accessdate=2015-07-23|work=The Guardian|agency=Reuters|date=2015-06-26|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627150014/http://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/jun/26/mainz-gonzalo-jara-edinson-cavani-bottom|dead-url=no}}</ref>

